notes.title: Take a shower
notes.content: I take a shower and get dressed. (Me ducho y me visto.)

notes.title: Brush my teeth
notes.content: I brush my teeth and wash my face. (Me cepillo los dientes y me lavo la cara.)

notes.title: Like to sleep
notes.content: On weekends, I like to sleep in and have a leisurely breakfast. (Los fines de semana, me gusta dormir más y desayunar sin prisa.

notes.title: Spend time with
notes.content: I spend time with family and friends or engage in hobbies. (Paso tiempo con la familia y amigos o practico mis aficiones.)

notes.title: Relax and watch TV
notes.content: In the evening, I relax and watch TV or read a book. (Por la noche, me relajo y veo televisión o leo un libro.)

notes.title: Comb my hair
notes.content: I comb my hair and apply some moisturizer. (Me peino y me aplico un poco de crema hidratante.)

notes.title: Go to the gym
notes.content: After work/school, I go to the gym or do some exercise. (Después del trabajo/escuela, voy al gimnasio o hago ejercicio.)

notes.title: Have meetings
notes.content: In the afternoon, I usually have meetings or classes. (Por la tarde, normalmente tengo reuniones o clases.)

notes.title: Have lunch
notes.content: I have lunch at 12 p.m. (Almuerzo a las 12 p.m.)
